{"tid":1670611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人長期每日食十幾廿粒安眠藥","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T08:33:31.000Z","uid":117238,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1d559ef38a2ce952388de6aff4f1e5c3c1861a","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:56:58.000Z","msg":"呀媽長期食開安眠藥 但佢從來唔講<br />\n後尾發現仲要係一日十粒以上 有唔開心事or大壓力可以上到廿粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為由細到大單親 聽返親戚講佢自從離婚後就有食<br />\n到後來工作壓力大 變左愈食愈多<br />\n兩年前有段時間好嚴重 返工日夜顛倒+食埋藥 係會去到斷片、口齒不清、神智不清訓著左係地下都唔知<br />\n果陣我仲返緊學又頂唔順佢咁樣 溝通唔到大家日日嘈都好崩潰 佢又死都唔肯睇醫生<br />\n到後尾佢轉左工 我又出左黎做野 好似好左好多 起碼無左以上情況<br />\n<br />\n近期問起 佢會話戒左好多啦 係咁叫我唔洗理佢<br />\n但後尾比我發現佢係講大話<br />\n叫過佢去睇醫生 但佢都係堅持唔想理 仲話都係得返十幾年命叫我放過佢唔好逼佢<br />\n<br />\n長期咁搞我自己對住佢都情緒好差 好燥底<br />\n<br />\n到前幾日 我地又嘈交 因為佢呢半年極沉迷買水晶野<br />\n應承左我好多次 （佢由細呃過我好多次）<br />\n最後都係選擇講大話問我借錢<br />\n嘈完之後 佢為講大話道歉 但又會講埋啲奇怪野<br />\nEg 我知你覺得我唔死都無用 之類嘅說話<br />\n後尾我搵親戚幫手搵下佢 確保佢無做傻事先<br />\n依家我地冷戰緊 但我覺得咁落去真係唔掂<br />\n<br />\n我甚至覺得自己都比佢逼到有情緒問題<br />\n夜晚會喪喊 停唔到 返工放工一諗起都忍得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有咩辦法？應該叫佢直接睇精神科醫生處理藥物問題？定去情緒輔導？"},{"pid":"10b39f8f884b8781cc5bfe7713e9c5c0e0fd06f7","tid":1670611,"uid":226424,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"要睇醫生一日食咁多粒太多，長期依賴藥物唔係一時三刻可以戒到，試下幫佢慢慢戒搵其他寄託，或者佢有無親戚朋友可以幫手勸下？<br />\n<br />\n我feel到你都好大壓力，可以搵朋友傾下/ 打電話心理輔導/ 社工傾下，佢地應該有經驗"},{"pid":"9066546e91a5762689b1e11da3fb61ff7e255651","tid":1670611,"uid":126514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7ae916f968b240803c32e4724a8c74bac90628","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9066546e91a5762689b1e11da3fb61ff7e255651","tid":1670611,"uid":126514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"原來有人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見身邊有朋友都係單親但都可以開開心心<br />\n以為得自己係咁<br />\n<br />\n咁你諗住點處理？"},{"pid":"72a641ed5f0ae5df61b057a2ad470078b128f338","tid":1670611,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"睇到你個po先醒起我夠鐘食<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">感冒</span>藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a567b0d3ba21552908595b23918bb2677d15acbe","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"呢d要睇心理醫生，開頭會覺得無乜用，可能要做入院治療"},{"pid":"0e545cbabbd68e1305d7658f9bd412e2cb06ee23","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a567b0d3ba21552908595b23918bb2677d15acbe","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"呢d要睇心理醫生，開頭會覺得無乜用，可能要做入院治療"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"佢肯定唔會入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次講起精神科(關藥事）佢都好抗拒<br />\n好似唔想承認自己有情緒/精神病"},{"pid":"f5af6dc92b67ba25e4b575a9086c7204743febec","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a641ed5f0ae5df61b057a2ad470078b128f338","tid":1670611,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"睇到你個po先醒起我夠鐘食<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">感冒</span>藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁下次要記得食啦"},{"pid":"fbb50e62aa29b18470dc7e832b08dd63ccb09bcc","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e545cbabbd68e1305d7658f9bd412e2cb06ee23","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a567b0d3ba21552908595b23918bb2677d15acbe","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"呢d要睇心理醫生，開頭會覺得無乜用，可能要做入院治療"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"佢肯定唔會入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次講起精神科(關藥事）佢都好抗拒<br />\n好似唔想承認自己有情緒/精神病"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"慢慢引導佢，俾佢知道情緒病or精神病係生理問題，藥物同醫生可以幫到佢"},{"pid":"5fd11d959db88000f6885db88919ce727d332df1","tid":1670611,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"咁都未死得?"},{"pid":"6f00aa226df646fb4eb01ece5560ed41cd5a6bc8","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fd11d959db88000f6885db88919ce727d332df1","tid":1670611,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"咁都未死得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"把口就唔好咁臭啦<br />\n人地親人黎嫁，咁認真問"},{"pid":"66545b41b8c4fc766d2da3ab5bf121b5a0643de1","tid":1670611,"uid":248270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"遲早洗胃佢就會怕"},{"pid":"419f501bbe9c8443da5069f3891aa938eff04d17","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b39f8f884b8781cc5bfe7713e9c5c0e0fd06f7","tid":1670611,"uid":226424,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"要睇醫生一日食咁多粒太多，長期依賴藥物唔係一時三刻可以戒到，試下幫佢慢慢戒搵其他寄託，或者佢有無親戚朋友可以幫手勸下？<br />\n<br />\n我feel到你都好大壓力，可以搵朋友傾下/ 打電話心理輔導/ 社工傾下，佢地應該有經驗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"我知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢有睇過一次政府精神科<br />\n但返到黎又話唔鐘意個醫生又盛 又話人地根本唔係真心幫佢 啲藥換左又唔得（話會抽筋同痛）<br />\n之後話會靠自己戒 叫我放長雙眼睇<br />\n結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我叫佢轉醫生又唔肯 成日逃避想過得一日得日<br />\n但我覺得佢根本活得唔開心"},{"pid":"182b0cc24cf91e5405746dcabc8ac72d3e675020","tid":1670611,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d92a82d463eff23b1c74fc0f180962c551f54fcb","tid":1670611,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"你提到水晶個D, 宗教角度覺得有鬼"},{"pid":"460394485eb08eff38f183b3b3ade97abaa7eff3","tid":1670611,"uid":4382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都咁<br />\n好擔心佢返返下工會整親<br />\n雖然有去睇醫生但係成日嫌人廢嫌啲藥冇效"},{"pid":"88667aaf1b2d5e18c4ab6ff7c21b9c82b79c7b7f","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92a82d463eff23b1c74fc0f180962c551f54fcb","tid":1670611,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"你提到水晶個D, 宗教角度覺得有鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"佢未沉迷之前已經食左好多年了<br />\n我覺得係佢人生無咩寄托 好易迷信<br />\n所以就變到狂買控制唔到<br />\n一開始係手鍊 我覺得都無咩野 提下佢唔好買咁多<br />\n依家變成大細水晶球、座同晶柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85370332f8786f2a362fad7a065ee753f4fc4c49","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460394485eb08eff38f183b3b3ade97abaa7eff3","tid":1670611,"uid":4382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都咁<br />\n好擔心佢返返下工會整親<br />\n雖然有去睇醫生但係成日嫌人廢嫌啲藥冇效"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"中曬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都係睇完一兩次嫌人廢+唔係真心幫佢<br />\n又話啲藥唔啱食到腳痛抽筋<br />\n之後就唔肯去睇了"},{"pid":"fa510c1a387ab9a930423e78fdbf3452c6211b71","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb50e62aa29b18470dc7e832b08dd63ccb09bcc","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e545cbabbd68e1305d7658f9bd412e2cb06ee23","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a567b0d3ba21552908595b23918bb2677d15acbe","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"呢d要睇心理醫生，開頭會覺得無乜用，可能要做入院治療"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"佢肯定唔會入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次講起精神科(關藥事）佢都好抗拒<br />\n好似唔想承認自己有情緒/精神病"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"慢慢引導佢，俾佢知道情緒病or精神病係生理問題，藥物同醫生可以幫到佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"隔一排等大家冷靜完我會嘗試再同佢解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網物色緊啲情緒/精神健康中心打去問下"},{"pid":"aab753cf495980dac5e5ad98a766e93b6f000ae1","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa510c1a387ab9a930423e78fdbf3452c6211b71","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb50e62aa29b18470dc7e832b08dd63ccb09bcc","tid":1670611,"uid":282767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e545cbabbd68e1305d7658f9bd412e2cb06ee23","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"佢肯定唔會入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次講起精神科(關藥事）佢都好抗拒<br />\n好似唔想承認自己有情緒/精神病"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"慢慢引導佢，俾佢知道情緒病or精神病係生理問題，藥物同醫生可以幫到佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"隔一排等大家冷靜完我會嘗試再同佢解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網物色緊啲情緒/精神健康中心打去問下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯，要多d耐心，要穩定左你自己情緒先。加油"},{"pid":"c8b626f9e5a6f443bf3a8db80e0a7a0005895ae9","tid":1670611,"uid":28193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"呢D野要強硬D, 請一日假&quot;的&quot;佢一齊去睇醫生, 食藥要MON住。"},{"pid":"bcd8906d0bb96598644853d1a1f8e94f9d2e8bc4","tid":1670611,"uid":299057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"安眠藥有副作用,影響情緒. 先了解一下她吃的藥有什麼成份."},{"pid":"3dd218db11b7adc0392937db612ece59e30236eb","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd8906d0bb96598644853d1a1f8e94f9d2e8bc4","tid":1670611,"uid":299057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"安眠藥有副作用,影響情緒. 先了解一下她吃的藥有什麼成份."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"我今晚返去查下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但聽聞係都幾重手嘅藥黎<br />\n有親戚同我講返好耐以前都食同一隻 但已戒<br />\n因為果陣佢發現食三、四粒 個腦已經唔係好load到野<br />\n個女同佢講野係聽完唔記得曬果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢知道我媽食廿粒話簡直癡L線"},{"pid":"b744b73f9ac5cfdfe340d2ee234b8f048e87b8ba","tid":1670611,"uid":299057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dd218db11b7adc0392937db612ece59e30236eb","tid":1670611,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd8906d0bb96598644853d1a1f8e94f9d2e8bc4","tid":1670611,"uid":299057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"安眠藥有副作用,影響情緒. 先了解一下她吃的藥有什麼成份."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"我今晚返去查下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但聽聞係都幾重手嘅藥黎<br />\n有親戚同我講返好耐以前都食同一隻 但已戒<br />\n因為果陣佢發現食三、四粒 個腦已經唔係好load到野<br />\n個女同佢講野係聽完唔記得曬果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢知道我媽食廿粒話簡直癡L線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"今一粒係食, 食廿粒都係食. 最重要是叫得動她去看醫生."},{"pid":"97c9f44ae7340ea230973e85ee957ec3fe8dd976","tid":1670611,"uid":51233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"過來人經驗  有個朋友之前都係咁既情況<br />\n佢屋企人話唔想逼個仔去睇醫生<br />\n不過去到濫藥呢個地步 唔睇醫生既話搵人24小時mon住佢都冇用<br />\n因為佢只會當你係敵人 講咩都冇用 唔會開解到佢<br />\n佢會寧願信街邊既人講野都唔會信你任何一句話 包括屋企人<br />\n到最後呢位朋友仲覺得屋企人夾埋想屈佢入精神病院<br />\n<br />\n同埋見醫生一定要一齊見<br />\n唔可以俾佢自己一個去見醫生<br />\n佢自己去睇會隱瞞好多野<br />\n政府醫生唔會好細心咁去觀察呢個人有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n依家佢龍精虎猛  日日屌女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}